# 🛒 Product Service API

A scalable backend service for managing products in an e-commerce system using **Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and MVC architecture**.

---

## 📌 Overview

This service handles:
- Product creation and management
- Product search and filtering
- Category-based product organization
- Seller-linked product system

Built with scalability and modular architecture in mind.

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- REST API
- MVC Architecture

